# Local build and prod delivery (Ingwaz)

Thesis-site on **`https://ingwaz.space`** — **static** `frontend/dist`, no Laravel on v1.

1. Build locally: `cd frontend && npm run build` (with `frontend/.env.production`, `VITE_SITE_URL=https://ingwaz.space`).
2. Deliver **`frontend/dist/`** to **`/var/www/ingwaz/public/`** on VPS (`rsync` or `scp`).
3. **Do not** run `npm run build` on VPS by default.

## SSH

- Alias: **`ingwaz-vps`** — see `docs/ssh-config-snippet.conf`
- Server path: **`/var/www/ingwaz/public`**
- Deploy script: `./scripts/deploy-prod.sh` (rsync; on Windows use scp from docs/DEPLOY-VPS.md §3.2)

